Package: cellgpsr
Type: Package
Title: Cell-GPS R Companion for Spatial Transcriptomics Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Taobo Hu [aut, cre], Mengping Long [aut], Mats Nilsson [aut]
Maintainer: Taobo Hu <taobo.hu@scilifelab.se>
Authors@R: 
    c(
        person("Taobo", "Hu", email = "taobo.hu@scilifelab.se", role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("Mengping", "Long", email = "mengping.long@scilifelab.se", role = "aut"),
        person("Mats", "Nilsson", email = "mats.nilsson@scilifelab.se", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Provides functions to compute cophenetic structure scores and generate
    spatial topology visualizations for spatial transcriptomics datasets, including
    reviewer-facing workflows accompanying the Cell-GPS manuscript.
Depends:  
    R (>= 4.3)
